-- Mexico’s Infonavit Says It Reached Mortgage Record in 2011
-- B y   A d r i a n a   L o p e z   C a r a v e o
-- 2012-01-05T19:48:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-05/mexico-s-infonavit-says-it-reached-mortgage-record-in-2011.html
Infonavit ,  Mexico ’s largest
originator of mortgages, reached a record 501,292 home loans in
2011.  The figure surpassed the agency’s goal of 480,000 mortgages
for the year, Infonavit said in an e-mailed statement. Chief
Executive Officer Victor Borras said in a March 3 interview that
he expected 515,000 home loans for 2011.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Adriana Lopez Caraveo in Mexico City at 
